{"tha-ap90:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap90:0.2":"Timiravagga ","tha-ap90:0.3":"Saddasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap90:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap90:1.2":"vasami pannasanthare; ","tha-ap90:1.3":"Phussassa dhammam bhanato, ","tha-ap90:1.4":"sadde cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap90:2.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap90:2.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap90:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap90:2.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap90:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap90:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap90:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap90:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saddasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap90:5.1":"Saddasannakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}